---
const SYMPTOMS = [
  'Congestión nasal constante',
  'Estornudos repetidos',
  'Picazón en nariz, ojos o piel',
  'Tos, silbidos en el pecho o falta de aire',
  'Dermatitis, urticaria o brotes en la piel',
  'Cansancio o mal descanso por los síntomas',
  'Síntomas que aparecen y desaparecen sin explicación',
];
---
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-breath via-white to-brand-breath">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-white/75 ring-1 ring-brand-authority/10 shadow-line backdrop-blur">
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.7] bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_12%_18%,rgba(79,183,167,0.16),transparent_55%),radial-gradient(circle_at_88%_28%,rgba(139,214,203,0.16),transparent_52%)]"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div class="relative p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-2xl bg-brand-breath ring-1 ring-brand-authority/10 shadow-sm">
          <img
            src="/icon-symptoms.png"
            alt=""
            class="h-6 w-6 object-contain opacity-90"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-brand-authority text-center">
        ¿Te pasa algo de esto con frecuencia?
        </h2>
      </div>

    <ul class="grid gap-3 sm:gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 mb-8">
      {SYMPTOMS.map((Symptom) => (
        <li class="group flex gap-3 rounded-2xl bg-white/80 ring-1 ring-brand-authority/10 px-4 py-3 text-base sm:text-lg text-brand-technical shadow-sm transition-transform hover:-translate-y-[1px] hover:shadow-line">
          <span class="mt-0.5 grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-brand-clinical/25 text-brand-authority ring-1 ring-brand-authority/10 transition-colors group-hover:bg-brand-clinical/35">
            <svg
              aria-hidden="true"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              class="h-4 w-4"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
            >
              <path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="leading-snug">{Symptom}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-breath via-white to-brand-breath ring-1 ring-brand-authority/10 p-[1px]">
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-brand-authority text-center py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/90 shadow-sm">
        Podría tratarse de una alergia mal diagnosticada o mal tratada.
      </p>
    </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
